{"tid":2316000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國周二起大規模接種輝瑞疫苗　分2劑接種料28日見全效","createTime":"2020-12-07T14:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T14:39:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"adfd1de00738bb60191cdecbc883f0b759969c4e","tid":2316000,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2820000/2822147/vaccine_thumb_20201207_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2820000%2F2822147%2Fvaccine_thumb_20201207_S_1024.jpg&h=9a7c12b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肺炎疫情持續，英國將於星期二開始，正式為國民接種由美國輝瑞藥廠和德國夥伴公司BioNTech合作研發的新型冠狀病毒疫苗，當局將優先為80歲以上長者、前線醫護、護老院員工等接種。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報道，英國於2日宣布批准輝瑞疫苗緊急使用後，將計劃星期二開始為國民接種輝瑞藥廠及BioNTech合作研發的新冠疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，英國共訂購4000萬劑輝瑞疫苗，可供2000萬人接種。首批約有80萬劑，將陸續分發到全國。由於輝瑞疫苗必須儲存在攝氏零下70度的環境，在一般雪櫃只能存放5天，因此衛生部指初期將先約在50間醫院安排注射接種工作。首批訂購的疫苗，會讓80歲以上長者、前線醫護人員、護老院員工和院友等高危人士優先接種。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2820000/2822147/5_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2820000%2F2822147%2F5_1024.png&h=ffcdb2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有接種疫苗的人士都會有「接種卡」，顯示所接種的疫苗類型、批次號、接種日期等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2822147/【新冠疫苗】英國周二起大規模接種輝瑞疫苗%E3%80%80分2劑接種料28日見全效?mtc=10027\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2822147%2F%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E3%80%91%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%8C%E8%B5%B7%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E8%BC%9D%E7%91%9E%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%25E3%2580%2580%E5%88%862%E5%8A%91%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E6%96%9928%E6%97%A5%E8%A6%8B%E5%85%A8%E6%95%88%3Fmtc%3D10027&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7HaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=68a0bcb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2822147/【新冠疫苗】英國周二起大規模接種輝瑞疫苗%E3%80%80分2劑接種料28日見全效?mtc=10027</a>"},{"pid":"01e4f1483bb912c96d929d167af457895db4c28c","tid":2316000,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會變28日後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6ba6f9fa2f10f0f1b5794a979b2c174f239efc","tid":2316000,"uid":237459,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"英國已經贏咗了"},{"pid":"ed2bc1f01de62a0a5c945344e47b6195be73873c","tid":2316000,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e4f1483bb912c96d929d167af457895db4c28c","tid":2316000,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會變28日後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"反疫狗"},{"pid":"5757cb812b0cf5e0641e979185f64ce3bd6489f0","tid":2316000,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"01e4f1483bb912c96d929d167af457895db4c28c","tid":2316000,"uid":58630,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:09:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會變28日後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09188090c4ab6e3fd6426a0ee92a05e00870372","tid":2316000,"uid":361751,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:11:06.000Z","msg":"香港嘈緊掃唔掃code<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fcd7d19ea51b8bdb67ccf3ce4550471e96cfe0","tid":2316000,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:11:26.000Z","msg":"科技股drop to $0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgm